data.eml:eml: Chronicle of Nature - Phenology of Plants of FGBU GPZ Kologrivskij Les name after M.G. Sinicin

Plants Phenology dataset compiled in the context of Chronicle of Nature program in FGBU GPZ Kologrivskij Les name after M.G. Sinicin (Russian Federation) consisting of 77 records collected during 2 years between 2010 and 2011.
